title: Worms 3 v2.0.4
description: Worms 3 v2.0.4 - Who does not know this game? Yes, there are no people on the planet! Charming combat worms came to our Android smartphones. This is the third part of the saga, which in many reviews, was the best of all games in the series. On the pitch there are two teams of worms. Your task - to destroy the enemy team, using a variety of weapons, which in the game a lot. In addition, your "players" can hide behind the intricate plots levels
